Presence/absence data for the Carolina Wren in the USA

Presence/absence of the Carolina Wren Thryothorus ludovicianus at Breeding Bird Survey transects in 2006. These data are made available in the maxlike R package. See carw.data for more details. This module loads them data transform the coordinates to lat/longs and formats the data for use in a zoon workflow.

CarolinaWrenPA()
